[{"Id": 1016421, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": "Abul Abbas, Ahmad bin Ali bin Nuh, says: Abu Ahmad, Mohsin bin Abdul Hakam Sajari, stated before me and I have written from his original work that it is written in the book of Abi Nasr, Jafar bin Mohammad bin Hasan bin Hisaam, that this prayer is narrated from Abul Qasim, Husain bin Rauh, in the following method <Namaz-e-Be’sat-2>.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Ahmed bin Ali bin Rauh kehte hai keh is namaz ko Mohsin bin Abdul Hakeem Sajaree ne mere liye naql kiya hai aur mai ne isko unki kitaab se likha hai, woh kehte thay, mai ne is namaz ko kitaab Abu Nasr Ja’far bin Muhammad se likha hai, woh kehte thay keh yeh namaz Abul Qasim Husain bin Rauh ki taraf se <Namaz-e-Be’sat-2> saadir (bayaan) huwi hai.", "UrduDescription": "احمد بن علی بن روح کہتاہے اس نماز کو محسن بن عبدالحکیم سجری نے میرے لئے نقل کیا ہے اور میں نے اس کو اس کی کتاب سے لکھا ہے وہ کہتا تھا میں نے اس نماز کو کتاب ابونصر جعفر بن محمد سے لکھا ہے وہ کہتا تھا کہ یہ نماز ابوالقاسم حسین بن روح کی طرف سے <نمازِ بعثت-۲> صادر ہوئی ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRe